1. Itextsharp:
A free tool to generate pdf. easily to get started, but it lacks of virtulizarion tools which was provided by option 2.

2. PDFsharp and MigraDoc

it has the simillar features compared to Itextsharp, but has a doc viewer which is handy for designing the pdf.

